<DocsLayout
  title="hitlimit Documentation - Fast Rate Limiting for Node.js, Bun, Express, Fastify, Hono & NestJS"
  description="Complete guide to hitlimit rate limiter. Learn how to protect your APIs with high-performance rate limiting middleware for Express, Fastify, Hono, NestJS, Bun, and Elysia. 200K+ req/s with memory, SQLite, or Redis stores."
  keywords="hitlimit documentation, rate limit tutorial, express rate limit middleware, fastify rate limit plugin, fastify rate limiter, @fastify/rate-limit alternative, hono rate limiter, hono-rate-limiter alternative, hono middleware, nestjs throttler alternative, bun rate limiter, elysia rate limit, nodejs api protection, api rate limiting guide, redis rate limit, sqlite rate limit, brute force protection"
